Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いったい何が正解なんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}タイムラインに咲き乱れるFAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:23.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絶望や歓喜なんて  駆け抜けるだけのMirage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溢れるインフォメーション  揺らいでいるノンフィクション
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赤い冷静  青い情熱  曖昧な審判（ジャッジ）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見透かしちゃうジーザス飼い馴らし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無関心ヴィーナス気取ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷走幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:41.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溺れていたいんでしょ  妄想はいつだって蜜の味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:47.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃ物足んないなら…「本能」（はだ）を曝せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さぁ、Naked  Dive！感情を放って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確かめろ君のREALを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう、Naked  Dive！衝動のMyself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求め続ければいいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  無我夢中で叫べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  限界はないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  その真理（こたえ）の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  拓けNew  world！
Comment: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:45.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————OPCN————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}究竟何為正解？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:17.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在時間線上爭奇鬥豔的虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:23.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕望和歡喜  只不過是穿插而過的幻景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滿溢而出的資訊  搖搖欲墜的認知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紅色代表冷靜  藍色代表熱情  這曖昧不清的判定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掌控洞悉一切的耶穌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假冒冰冷美豔的維納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷茫幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:41.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要沉溺於其中吧  妄想無論何時都如蜜之味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:47.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若是還不夠的話…那就把「本能」都展現出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧  Naked  Dive！  將感情釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去確定屬於你的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯  Naked  Dive！  不斷追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}屬於自己內心的那份衝動不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  盡情地呼喊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  沒有任何界限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  邁向那片真理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  開拓新的世界！
Comment: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:09.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,————————EDJP————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:16.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,新しいわたしで どんなときも向き合いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:19.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなで笑顔になれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:32.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,好きなことができてたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:37.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,一方通行じゃやっぱ ものたりないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:40.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かに伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,嬉しすぎると泣けちゃうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しすぎると笑っちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:50.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな毎日にトクンてきてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:53.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぼんやりふくらんだ夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:56.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとすぐ破裂しちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:59.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,悔しかったあの日のPain　(No need!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,掴むべきは　これからのShine　(Yes!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:04.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　(Yes!)　叶えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:06.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぜったいにできるって！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,鳥が空とぶように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:12.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,星が夜をかざるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,当たり前みたいに いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:17.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かに見てもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:19.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:25.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ白なこころで迎えた朝は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:25.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ハツラツだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:28.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}だから元気をおくろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(200,0)}All right!　変わってく景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:33.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}Always!　一緒にみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}All right!　もちろん全力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(0,200)}Always!　純真で　It's all right!
Comment: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:09.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————EDCN————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:16.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想无时无刻以全新的自己面对一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:19.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起冁然而笑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:32.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对于爱不释手的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:37.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,光是独享 果然是远远不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:40.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想要将其分享给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,喜极而泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:45.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,悲中苦笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:50.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,每一天都令人期待不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:53.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不明不白膨胀的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:56.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会马上破灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:59.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔过去的痛苦 （没必要！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,该牢牢握住的是未来的曙光 （Yes!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:04.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 （Yes!） 一定能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:06.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,必定会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如同翱翔于天际的小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:12.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛点缀于夜空的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时都理所当然地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:17.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想要让别人也一起欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:19.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:25.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,以纯白内心所迎接的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:25.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么令人精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:28.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}所以  想将活力赠于你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(200,0)}All  right!  不断变化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:33.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}Always!  想要与你一起观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}All  right!  当然会全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(0,200)}Always!  维持纯真便行了!
Comment: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,————————Text————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  喜欢温泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖和又舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要泡在温泉里就会觉得很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻人类从太古时代开始就使用温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些古老文献上也有记载此事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本  大约有三千处以上的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说年间大约有一亿人以上使用温泉设施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在大多以观光和美容等休闲娱乐为主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在以前  为了健康去泡温泉的温泉疗法是很常见的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如  通过泡高温温泉可以促进血液循环
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调节副交感神经
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实证明温泉不仅有改善心情  还有强身益体的功效
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位坂本龙马和他妻子龙氏一起的温泉疗养之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是日本人最初的蜜月旅行  而远近闻名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  温泉有着治愈身心的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这次正好是和温泉有关的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  在海外还盛行着「饮泉」这一治疗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如字面所述  就是把温泉喝下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也有温泉是不能喝的  要多注意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我亲自喝下试试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦你打算喝那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  我准备的是能喝的
Comment: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,————————TextA————————
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选出五个球  然后考虑它们的排放顺序就是排列
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45}你从刚才开始就在干什么呢  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45}我正在研究新的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做「亚伯梅林之指」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过非常地难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(474,1020)}排列需要排放顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而组合只要选择就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  今天还真是异常地热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出大事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是上课的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面外面  中庭那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温~泉~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为这玩意才那么热的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是件严重的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是那只phantom搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那只猴子先生挖出的这个温泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  包括那些小猴子和温泉在内全部都是phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想脱了衣服去泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  太丢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来课只能停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  让我去把身上的汗洗洗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  能封印它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不画出全身像  是没法封印的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡在水里的部分看不见  不知道什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  真是没用啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈你呢  可以吞噬它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  必须要对方弱化到一定程度才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:05:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话没法开始上课  就只能暑假再来补习了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不愿意的话  大家就去全力消灭那只phantom吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全甩给我们了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我们怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个我上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  解决掉它  上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞舞之翼  飘落之翼  降临之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以汝钢之利爪将邪恶使者撕碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二个我上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩虹雷电
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度相当快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是我登场的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔介  上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧吧  燃烧吧  我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在此  完成真正的超绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到水  当然得由我们海滩天使出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水龙之缚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激流之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺穿它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长学姐们这么轻易就被打败了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只phantom好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还很好色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于轮到最后的王牌登场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久瑠美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  温泉可不像平地脚下那么稳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕过去  从背后进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开我  你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现身  马加锡亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  去救舞学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多小狗小猫都是很讨厌洗澡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胀起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子正在吸水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得软趴趴的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸同学  你行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启之拓之创之放之  天地开合之韵律！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻之觅之探之索之  束其形于原地！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  温泉成了厚重的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用锁链无法束缚住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道小糸非常怕热？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你也是  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下头疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎所有的学生都被打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能靠近它来个突然袭击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的招数应该能打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1  2…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这东西是从哪里找来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向戏剧部借的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要装成马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫做特洛伊木马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在希腊神话中的特洛伊战争里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了骗过以防守引以为豪的特洛伊城的守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥德修斯造了一匹巨大的木马…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西就不必说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好走路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在走  是舞学姐你太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就这样笔直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意别被它发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在接近它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从背后给它来上一击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啊  你干嘛停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很重  没法往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在往下沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞姐姐
Comment: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,————————TextB————————
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上泳衣凉快多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  幸好游泳课程已经开课了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸同学  已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这次我一定会打败它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只phantom估计是水属性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得小糸同学你的火是对付不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要草率出手的好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去不也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能把它引出温泉  我就能封印它了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  既然这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你能到我这边来  我会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子能顺利把它引出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈  你这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这样  像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰  腰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和猴子先生做好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会  我都那么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许它没感觉到玲奈有多少魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就差一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  久瑠美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用黄金熊爪（耙子）吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  自从从熊的世界回来之后就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用这个代替
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金熊爪（耙子）…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小糸你很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸你行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸同学  多笑笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像玲奈那样  给它抛媚眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛媚眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神上扬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媚眼抛出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉更加毛骨悚然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样就像女混混
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再性感一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把舌头露点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样  像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不可爱呢  露太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手做邀约它的姿势  勾它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是找它单挑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能用那招了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那招？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发情期的母猴子  屁股会变红
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们靠露出红屁股来诱惑雄性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只要把屁股涂红…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  然后最适合的人选是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是舞学姐  一定能顺利引出phantom的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都已经被舔过两次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必帮下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被那只phantom袭击你也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在变成那样之前  我一定会把它封印的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做就做谁怕谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  晴彦  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再激烈一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是个屁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦你拿着画笔  就不想把一切都宣泄到画布上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对画的爱就只有这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看它啊  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这涂上去的爽快感是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刷子像跳舞一般舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么地柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柔软啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是最高级的画布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西真的能诱惑它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  也没必要非要晴彦来涂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下来才是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  小舞超有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要能看到大猴子的脚就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞学姐  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我素描本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被油漆全染红了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  只好碰碰运气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸圣祀  诸生献  诸静奉  神之祷言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZAZAS  ZAZAS  NASNAZAS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现身  克苏鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为又要被舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  那只章鱼先生是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是魔导书「死灵之书」上所记载的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:16.02,English,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017,952.5)}Necronomicon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君临于太古地球的伟大邪神克苏鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚是怎样召唤它的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫亚伯梅林之指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有画也能召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为之前发生过没有素描本无法召唤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一直在练习这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克苏鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈  你能吞噬掉它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点没有食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确看上去很难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只好烧掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只猴子先生好像在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢  是发生了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆跑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才泡温泉来治疗心理创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为泡温泉不是能让人平静下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那哭难道是觉得我被晴彦抢走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都无所谓了  接下来该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能抚慰那只大猴子的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许就能阻止温泉化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:21:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  要有人去做猴子先生的新娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的话我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是戏剧部的服装？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像很中意你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来救我的时候  还是挺帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  这玩过火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来  谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:04.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,
